column5: Hey folks, i put my trail camera out last thursday evening and went back to get it today, memory was full!    Nothing great on it but had lots of doe pics and some decent bucks, not sure any of them are the ONE but might work. Here they are:         The flies were really making a meal of this guy alot  Archery season starts September 25th, cant wait!  cheers, jason
caption "what the hell is that? a camera? hey fly's check this out.."

Nice shots! Those will be some nice bucks come fall! I'm going to put mine out soon as well. Aslo plan on planting a small area with clover. Can't wait for hunting! But I can deal with fishing until then..lol
got a few to add from my trail cam
